Wolfblade/ Organics:

Wolfblade had somehow escaped without injury.  She looked around at the changed landscape, at the devastation that abounded.  She pushed heself to her feet slowly, in shock over the sheer destruction.  She wandered around, aimlessly, until she stumbled onto Organics, in stasis lock.  It took a moment to register, but she snapped back to reality.
&quot;Windlord!  Organics is hurt bad!&quot;

Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:
: : Rodimus Prime/Kup/Darkangel/DeathStar/SharpClaws/Wolfenstein : :

After realizing that most of the troops didn&#39;t escape the blast Rodimus turns around. He drives up to the blast site looking for injured bots. The cannon was nothing but rubble now.

Kup follows Rodimus.

Darkangel and DeathStar had flown up to escape the explosion. They came down and landed.

The four bots transformed to bot mode.

Kup: So much for the cannon, lads.

Rodimus Prime: If you can respond do so. Anyone whos walking, help the injured.

Both SharpClaws and Wolfenstein were blown from the site and were laying on the outskirts of the battlefield. They were heavily damaged. Wolf was still functioning but had fallen into stasis lock. SharpClaws would terminate soon.


